The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques for summarizing tabular data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for recommending types for text segments, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely category. The use of a knowledge base and ontology suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.DB (Databases) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), which deal with knowledge representation and reasoning. Finally, the paper involves machine learning techniques for generating the summary, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another possible category.
